872
00:51:32,460 --> 00:51:34,310
My treat. Don't worry.

873
00:51:34,320 --> 00:51:35,310
Here.

874
00:51:36,130 --> 00:51:37,810
It's for coffee.

875
00:51:38,500 --> 00:51:41,020
With me, you don't have to worry about money.

876
00:51:41,030 --> 00:51:43,290
I have plenty of money.

877
00:51:45,500 --> 00:51:48,720
