882
00:52:06,730 --> 00:52:10,810
Order whatever you want.
My treat.

883
00:52:10,820 --> 00:52:12,310
Okay.

884
00:52:12,320 --> 00:52:14,740
When I get stressed out,

885
00:52:14,760 --> 00:52:18,190
I come here and order whatever I want.

886
00:52:20,360 --> 00:52:22,620
Say ah!

887
00:52:23,260 --> 00:52:24,950
I can eat it myself.

888
00:52:24,960 --> 00:52:27,640
Don't say no.

889
00:52:27,650 --> 00:52:29,610
Ah!

890
00:52:35,650 --> 00:52:38,910
How cute!

891
00:52:38,920 --> 00:52:43,610
I don't think you'd stab a woman in her back.

892
00:52:51,690 --> 00:52:55,140
I like you.

893
00:52:55,150 --> 00:52:56,540
Do you like me?

894
00:52:56,550 --> 00:52:58,080
Well...

895
00:52:58,090 --> 00:52:59,810
