896
00:52:59,820 --> 00:53:01,310
I agree.

897
00:53:01,320 --> 00:53:04,510
So let's meet every day from now on.

898
00:53:08,550 --> 00:53:10,040
Oh, my!

899
00:53:10,050 --> 00:53:12,220
Stop this!

