00:53:12,230 --> 00:53:13,410
Man!

901
00:53:14,820 --> 00:53:16,120
Miran!

902
00:53:16,130 --> 00:53:17,250
Eun Miran!

903
00:53:17,550 --> 00:53:19,640
She hasn't come home yet.

904
00:53:20,420 --> 00:53:22,410
This is nuts.

905
00:53:44,190 --> 00:53:47,140
He's at the summer house right now.

906
00:53:47,150 --> 00:53:49,410
His phone is still off.

907
00:53:50,050 --> 00:53:52,010
From what the maids are doing,

908
