909
00:54:02,730 --> 00:54:04,290
I think this is enough.

910
00:54:05,630 --> 00:54:07,990
Why don't we give it another day?

911
00:54:08,000 --> 00:54:08,990
No.

912
00:54:26,530 --> 00:54:27,950
What are you going to do?

913
00:54:29,820 --> 00:54:32,410
Should I go get him?

914
00:54:32,420 --> 00:54:35,610
So you can beat him up?

915
00:54:37,690 --> 00:54:39,840
There's no need for that.

916
00:54:40,590 --> 00:54:43,310
I was being stupid.

917
00:54:43,320 --> 00:54:45,220
Now I know for sure,

918
00:54:46,730 --> 00:54:49,350
