919
00:54:49,360 --> 00:54:50,520
I have no regrets.

920
00:55:12,730 --> 00:55:13,850
Ms. Eun.

921
00:55:28,690 --> 00:55:30,280
What are you doing?

922
00:55:35,260 --> 00:55:37,450
Get out of my house!

923
00:55:43,820 --> 00:55:46,620
I'm sorry. Forgive me.

924
00:55:46,630 --> 00:55:48,190
I'm really sorry.

925
00:55:48,190 --> 00:55:50,410
You weren't home and I was in a hurry.

926
00:55:51,090 --> 00:55:54,490
I have no time to explain anything.

927
00:55:54,500 --> 00:55:55,890
Don't ask me any questions.

928
00:55:55,900 --> 00:55:57,390
Just lend me $50,000.

929
00:55:59,530 --> 00:56:04,120
I know I shouldn't ask for money before we're married,

930
00:56:04,130 --> 00:56:05,750
