954
00:57:37,630 --> 00:57:41,250
Miran, I mean, director!

955
00:57:41,260 --> 00:57:43,790
Please!

956
00:57:43,800 --> 00:57:46,750
A person's life is on the line.

957
00:57:46,760 --> 00:57:49,120
She might die,

958
00:57:49,130 --> 00:57:51,810
