959
00:57:53,760 --> 00:57:56,990
I'll do anything you want.

960
00:57:57,000 --> 00:57:59,250
Please,

961
00:57:59,260 --> 00:58:01,450
please help me.

962
00:58:04,960 --> 00:58:09,120
I'm not asking for it.
 Let me borrow it.

963
00:58:09,130 --> 00:58:11,220
