964
00:58:11,860 --> 00:58:13,220
My wife is...

965
00:58:13,230 --> 00:58:14,640
Stop.

966
00:58:15,260 --> 00:58:17,090
You're so boring.

967
00:58:17,760 --> 00:58:21,090
I thought you were different.

968
